<p>This Privacy Policy sets forth the privacy practices in effect at EBSCO Information Service&rsquo;s websites, including our Careers Site <a href="https://careers.ebscoind.com/ebscoinformationservices" target="_blank">https://www.ebsco.com/careers</a> (the &ldquo;Websites&rdquo;) and information gathered when you initiate requests for information regarding our products or services.. The Websites do not include those sites which host our products, services and applications, which are governed by their own privacy policies.&nbsp; If you do not agree to these terms, do not access these Websites.<br />
